                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430508-name-1602" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430508-name-1602" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430508-name-1602" type="surname" value="ELWORTHY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430508-name-1602" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>RICHARD ELWORTHY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a cowkeeper, and live at Bermondsey. The prisoner was in my service. I missed a spoon about one o'clock on Thursday last—I had not seen it since the Monday—this it it—I have the fellow to it in my pocket.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
