                        <interp inst="t18430508-name-1603" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE POOLE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a pawnbroker, and live in New Park-street. The prisoner came to my shop, and offered to pawn this spoon, on Thursday last—he asked 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. for it—he said it was his own, and it appeared as if it had just been used—I stopped it—he had a horse and cart with him—the prose<lb></lb>cutor's name was on the cart.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I did not take it to the shop. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> I am certain it was him—he said he gave 6<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. to a pawnbroker for it.</p>
